it services stanford university bcas meditation info page bcas meditation about bcas meditation english usa last updated on sat oct 2 18 56 58 1999 welcome to the mailing list for the buddhist community at stanford currently we use this list to post announcements for upcoming events discussions and other postings may be held on future lists to see the collection of prior postings to the list visit the bcas meditation archives the current archive is only available to the list members using bcas meditation to post a message to all the list members send email to bcas meditation lists stanford edu you can subscribe to the list or change your existing subscription in the sections below subscribing to bcas meditation subscribe to bcas meditation by filling out the following form you will be sent email requesting confirmation to prevent others from gratuitously subscribing you this is a private list which means that the list of members is not available to non members your email address your name optional which language do you prefer to display your messages english usa would you like to receive list mail batched in a daily digest no yes bcas meditation subscribers the subscribers list is only available to the list members enter your address and password to visit the subscribers list address password for non stanford edu address only to unsubscribe from bcas meditation get a password reminder or change your subscription options enter your subscription email address if you leave the field blank you will be prompted for your email address bcas meditation list run by hannahky at stanford edu jfouse at stanford edu oshidary at stanford edu rnie at stanford edu sinyee at stanford edu wongss at stanford edu ykchia at stanford edu bcas meditation administrative interface requires authorization overview of all lists stanford edu mailing lists
